name: Hua Charm Necklaces
description:
Our hand stamped Hua Charm necklaces say a lot with one word.

KAI nvs. Sea, sea-water; area near the sea, sea side, lowlands; tide, current in the sea.

OLA nvs. Life, health, well-being, living, livelihood, means of support, salvation.

HĀ nvs. To breathe, exhale; to breathe upon; breath, life.

Which hua (word) means the most to you?

18" chain.  Sterling Silver.

Donʻt forget! You can customize these charms to say anything you want with a maximum of 5 letters.  Just contact us.
